 ICS 8 - Introduction to Computer Security Homework 7, 50 Points
 
Due: Tuesday, November 23, 2010, at the beginnning of class 
 

 
   
Describe the pattern of how you use your computer during this week,
how you are likely to use your computer next week (including during
the week of Thanksgiving), how you are likely to use your computer
during finals week, and how you are likely to use your computer after
finals week. Explain how these differing patterns would impact an
intrusion detection system that has learned your usage pattern based
on the first week mentioned above.
20 points.
  
